# Generative notation

* Adds arithmetics and programmatic features:
  * Random numbers: **% ? (0,9) (0.1,0.5)**
  * Repeats: **[: :]**
  * Transformations **(list)<...>(parameters)**
```
zplay "% ? % ? % ?"
#zplay "[: 0 3 2 :]"
#zplay "[: (1,3) (4,6) :]"
#zplay "(:  (1,3) (4,6) :)"
#zplay "(0 1 (1,4))+(0,3)"
#zplay "(1..3)<+>(? 4)"
```